@node Synopsis
@section Synopsis
This package lets you handle i.e.@ start, restart devcontainers of your
projects and forwards all your @code{compile} commands into the
devcontainer by advising @code{compilation-start}. So as long you use
@code{compile} to build, test and run (parts of your) software, all will
be executed inside the devcontainer.

