@node Development
@section Development
This package uses unit tests defined by Emacs' built in
@uref{https://www.gnu.org/software/emacs/manual/html_mono/ert.html,ERT}
testing framework. An easy way to run the tests is
@uref{https://github.com/rejeep/ert-runner.el,ert-runnerel}. To run the
test suite from the command line simply

@itemize
@item
Install @uref{https://github.com/cask/cask,Cask} on your system
@item
Open a shell in the repo's root directory
@item
Install the rependencies using
@end itemize

@verbatim
$ cask install
@end verbatim

@itemize
@item
Run the test suite using
@end itemize

@verbatim
$ cask exec ert-runner
@end verbatim

If you want to run the tests interactively from within emacs, you might
want to take a look at
@uref{https://github.com/johannes-mueller/test-cockpit.el,test-cockpitel}.
